description: Smart. Handmade. Cuisine. NEPA'S only gourmet food truck!Sometimes you’re just hungry for fresh, hand built food made with smart ingredients. You want memorable cuisine, you want great food but you don’t want to follow a dress code. And you're right, putting on your big boy pants for a meal does not create the great dining experience. Who says upscale has gotta be so uppity? Its not a crime that your palate has EVOLVED beyond that of the “traditional” and “classical” eye-talian joint. Now what? At WTF, we love a good meatball as much as the next guy but we think the people need some options. So let's change this up and throw your taste buds a bit of a party. Call it what you want... New American, Street food, or Bistro fare. We’re just here to serve up some of the tastiest and unconventional food you’ve ever ordered... from a big green truck. Just don’t ask for silverware (they’re plastic sporks) because we eat with our HANDS! No need to fret, we've got LOTS of napkins.
name: What The FORK
